metadata.name: Immortal Artifact
metadata.description:
Get your face fucked up by the godfather of Surrealist manga.

Kago combines human anatomy and surrealist influences in his detailed psychedelic illustrations, with his unmistakable "monster girls" never failing to shock audiences with their violent beauty. The manga legend combines inspirations from cult slasher films, 1920s ero guro and modern cultural influences into the iconic style that makes him one of Japan's most popular artists.

Now, collectors of Kago's work have become a part of his work, with the modern master taking commissions for a limited number of custom PFP NFTs.
